@startuml Weaviate Schema Creation State Machine
[*] --> CollectionUnchecked : Provider Instantiated

CollectionUnchecked --> CheckingCollection : ensureCollectionExists() called

CheckingCollection --> CollectionExists : collections.exists(collectionName) == true
CheckingCollection --> CreatingCollection : collections.exists(collectionName) == false

CreatingCollection --> CollectionExists : collections.create() succeeds
CreatingCollection --> SchemaError : throws Exception

CollectionExists --> InitializingSequence : fetchObjects() to find max ID
InitializingSequence --> ProviderReady : sequence initialized

SchemaError --> [*]
ProviderReady --> [*]
@enduml
